                  <sense n="1" xml:id="D1">
                     <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                        <quote>lucens</quote>
                     </cit>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ከመ፡ ይኩና፡ አዕይንቲከ፡ ብሩሃተ፡ ላዕለ፡ ቤት፡ </foreign>
